text: Declan Keilty (born 8 May 1995) is an Australian rules footballer who plays for the Melbourne Football Club in the Australian Football League (AFL). He was selected at pick #41 in the 2017 rookie draft. He made his senior debut against Hawthorn in round 7 of the 2019 season.
